import React from 'react'

const CasesByCountry = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>#</th>
                    <th>Country</th>
                    <th>Total Cases</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <tr></tr>
                </tr>
            </thead>
        </>
    )
}
export default CasesByCountry;
